highlights.text: “Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Delhi the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“SPAIN” by Jassa Dhillon and thiarajxtt is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Delhi, up 40 spots at #25.
Karan Aujla has the most spots on Top Songs Delhi. “Players” is the highest at #8.
“Take It Easy” by Karan Aujla and Ikky is the highest new entry on Top Songs Delhi at #52.
